data.description: This charming home boasts four bedrooms and two-and-a-half baths, providing ample space for comfortable living. The large family room is a standout feature, featuring an open floor plan, cathedral ceilings, and a cozy gas fireplace that creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The formal living room and dining room offer additional spaces for entertaining or more intimate gatherings. The well-appointed eat-in kitchen comes complete with all stainless steel appliances, adding a touch of modernity to the heart of the home. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, equipped with a full bathroom that includes a luxurious jetted tub and convenient double vanity sinks. The fenced backyard provides a private oasis, wonderful for outdoor activities and entertaining guests. The property has a sprinkler system and well, both convey "as is". This home combines functionality, style, and comfort for a delightful living experience.
